PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773609115
OL,3,CFive men jailed for more than 80 years
OL,4,Cafter man stabbed at caravan site
OL,6,FThe woman, aged in her 20s, escaped
OL,7,Fthrough a window, while the man ran
OL,8,Fout of the caravan. But the victim,
OL,9,Falso aged in his 20s, was stabbed
OL,10,Fseveral times.
OL,12,FThe group fled the site as police
OL,13,Flaunched an investigation. This led to
OL,14,Ffour members of the Galbraith family
OL,15,Fbeing arrested: James, 29; Michael,
OL,16,F27; Thomas, 24; and Anthony, 21.
OL,18,FThey were each charged with attempted
OL,19,Fmurder and making threats to kill and
OL,20,Fremanded to prison.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
