FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773609115
OL,3,CFive men jailed for more than 80 years
OL,4,Cafter man stabbed at caravan site
OL,6,FAfter further investigation, we
OL,7,Fcharged James Galbraith, 49, and
OL,8,FThomas McDonagh, 54, with conspiring
OL,9,Fto pervert the course of justice.
OL,11,FFollowing a seven-week trial at
OL,12,FWarwick Crown Court that finished in
OL,13,FJanuary, five of the men were found
OL,14,Fguilty.
OL,16,FWhile the judge directed the jury to
OL,17,Ffind James Galbraith, 29, not guilty
OL,18,Fof attempted murder and making threats
OL,19,Fto kill.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
