OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773609115
OL,3,CFive men jailed for more than 80 years
OL,4,Cafter man stabbed at caravan site
OL,6,FAnd yesterday, Friday, March 13, at
OL,7,FWarwick Crown Court, the men were
OL,8,Fsentenced to:
OL,10,FSpeaking after the case, Detective
OL,11,FConstable Chloe Butcher, who was the
OL,12,Fofficer in charge of the case, said:
OL,13,F"This has been a thorough and careful
OL,14,Finvestigation with many complexities.
OL,16,F"The lengthy prison sentences handed
OL,17,Fdown today reflect the seriousness of
OL,18,Fwhat happened.
